                         A3 = c(1,2,4,5,7))
        
        t2<- data.frame(B2 = c(""""black"""", """"pink"""", """"lime"""", """"green"""", """"grey"""", """"mist"""", """"blond"""", """"grass"""", """"violet"""", """"red""""),
                        B3 = c(""""a"""", """"b"""", """"a"""", """"c"""", """"d"""", """"d"""", """"a"""" , """"c"""", """"a"""", """"b""""))
        
        > t1
              A1     A2 A3

        3  green yellow  4
        4 yellow  black  5
        5  brown   <NA>  7
        > t2
               B2 B3
        1   black  a
        2    pink  b
        3    lime  a
